author: jaz
msg: tracking codes now support -1 lifetime (just for the session), which will create a session cookie, instead of a persistent cookie. Remove setVersion(1) when setting cookies since this is "experimental" and 1) is not used for other cookies in OFbiz 2) does not work with Safari
Added new TrackingCodeType 'ACCESS' to represent an access code.
Added new preprocessor event to restrict access to an application to users with a valid ACCESS tracking code.
